Obama’s 2008 campaign memory is a sad reminder of what could have happened
Nathaniel P. Morris is a 2nd year medical student at Harvard Medical School.
I’m reading a sad book these days.
It is a book that I thought would encourage me during the sluggishness of the 2nd year of medicine and give me hope.
